      "file_path": "healthcheck-container/Dockerfile",
      "patchset_number": 2,
      "line": 19,
      "message": "Major release 10 is the current \"long-term support\" release, major release 8 was the previous \"long-term support\" release.\n(If I recall correctly, node versioning isn't strictly semantic versioning.)",
